Text: RE Storage SampleI will definitely work on it Thank you for your feedback Original Message From Grigsby Mike Sent Tuesday November PM To Shim Elizabeth Holst Keith Subject RE Storage Sample Is this report ready to be published daily I would update the storage info at the bottom Use the current storage balance for each facility include a column showing daily activity and show the maximum capacity and daily injwd capacity Keith will help you with this data Thanks Mike Original Message From Shim Elizabeth Sent Tue PM To Grigsby Mike Cc Subject FW Storage Sample Hi Mike just wanted to show you what I sent Keith last week Im working on getting more info and also working on cut codes with Chris Hyde and Matt pena UNIFYIT Thank you Liz Original Message From Shim Elizabeth Sent Tuesday November PM To Holst Keith Subject Storage Sample Keith I changed the report information as you requested Please let me know if there are additional changes you need On some of the storage points the current balance information is not available I will work towards getting these in the meantime let me know what else would be needed ES CURVEMASTERxls
